{"type":"text","timestamp":1778379351832,"sessionID":"ses_1f054e4cbffebD7Q6EmicnVKj8","part":{"id":"prt_e0fab613a001hquRYAZEoAJ0uZ","messageID":"msg_e0fab4ec8001wCUtabTBqhBwv4","sessionID":"ses_1f054e4cbffebD7Q6EmicnVKj8","type":"text","text":"The issue is clear enough to investigate: UBERON currently asserts `foramen secundum part_of atrial septum secundum`, while the comment argues the foramen secundum is in/part of septum primum and the NCIT reverse relationship is also wrong. I’ll inspect the relevant term stanzas and supporting parent terms before editing.","time":{"start":1778379350330,"end":1778379351830},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0868e9d81e4e7f220169ffea5649ac819fb65d1eb5818d8a3e","phase":"commentary"}}}}
