{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778379546401,"sessionID":"ses_1f054e4cbffebD7Q6EmicnVKj8","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"apply_patch","callID":"call_ZXxDj3k71rPvn22hC7r7ZaNT","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"patchText":"*** Begin Patch\n*** Add File: /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n+Updated UBERON:0006678 so foramen secundum is defined as a foramen in the septum primum, with the logical `part_of` axiom changed from atrial septum secundum to atrial septum primum. Changes committed in PR #<NN>.\n*** Add File: /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/PR_COMMENTS.md\n+## Summary\n+\n+This PR addresses issue #3522 by correcting the UBERON representation of `foramen secundum` (`UBERON:0006678`).\n+\n+## Changes\n+\n+- Updated the text definition from \"A foramen in the septum secundum\" to \"A foramen in the septum primum\".\n+- Updated the logical definition from `part_of UBERON:0004155 ! atrial septum secundum` to `part_of UBERON:0004154 ! atrial septum primum`.\n+- Added a `term_tracker_item` link to issue #3522.\n+\n+## Rationale\n+\n+The issue discussion noted that the foramen secundum/ostium secundum forms in the septum primum, not in the septum secundum. This is also consistent with the existing `atrial septum primum` definition and the existing external definition on `UBERON:0006678`, which describes it as an opening perforating the septum primum.\n+\n+## Checklist Completed\n+\n+- Read the imported issue context and repository guidance.\n+- Checked relevant existing UBERON terms: `UBERON:0006678`, `UBERON:0004154`, `UBERON:0004155`, and `UBERON:0004111`.\n+- Checked the applicable DOSDP pattern for anatomical entities that are part of another anatomical entity.\n+- Reviewed the cited Wikipedia page for foramen secundum, which states it is in the septum primum and distinguishes it from the foramen ovale in the septum secundum.\n+- Edited via `obo-checkout.pl` and `obo-checkin.pl` rather than directly editing the main ontology file.\n+- Reserialized `src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo` with `robot convert`.\n+- Validated logical consistency with `robot reason --reasoner ELK`.\n+\n+@dragon-ai-agent\n*** End Patch"},"output":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\nA PR_COMMENTS.md","metadata":{"diff":"Index: /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n===================================================================\n--- /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n+++ /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,1 @@\n+Updated UBERON:0006678 so foramen secundum is defined as a foramen in the septum primum, with the logical `part_of` axiom changed from atrial septum secundum to atrial septum primum. Changes committed in PR #<NN>.\n\nIndex: /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/PR_COMMENTS.md\n===================================================================\n--- /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/PR_COMMENTS.md\n+++ /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/PR_COMMENTS.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,25 @@\n+## Summary\n+\n+This PR addresses issue #3522 by correcting the UBERON representation of `foramen secundum` (`UBERON:0006678`).\n+\n+## Changes\n+\n+- Updated the text definition from \"A foramen in the septum secundum\" to \"A foramen in the septum primum\".\n+- Updated the logical definition from `part_of UBERON:0004155 ! atrial septum secundum` to `part_of UBERON:0004154 ! atrial septum primum`.\n+- Added a `term_tracker_item` link to issue #3522.\n+\n+## Rationale\n+\n+The issue discussion noted that the foramen secundum/ostium secundum forms in the septum primum, not in the septum secundum. This is also consistent with the existing `atrial septum primum` definition and the existing external definition on `UBERON:0006678`, which describes it as an opening perforating the septum primum.\n+\n+## Checklist Completed\n+\n+- Read the imported issue context and repository guidance.\n+- Checked relevant existing UBERON terms: `UBERON:0006678`, `UBERON:0004154`, `UBERON:0004155`, and `UBERON:0004111`.\n+- Checked the applicable DOSDP pattern for anatomical entities that are part of another anatomical entity.\n+- Reviewed the cited Wikipedia page for foramen secundum, which states it is in the septum primum and distinguishes it from the foramen ovale in the septum secundum.\n+- Edited via `obo-checkout.pl` and `obo-checkin.pl` rather than directly editing the main ontology file.\n+- Reserialized `src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo` with `robot convert`.\n+- Validated logical consistency with `robot reason --reasoner ELK`.\n+\n+@dragon-ai-agent\n\n","files":[{"filePath":"/__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md","relativePath":"ISSUE_COMMENTS.md","type":"add","patch":"Index: /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n===================================================================\n--- /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n+++ /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,1 @@\n+Updated UBERON:0006678 so foramen secundum is defined as a foramen in the septum primum, with the logical `part_of` axiom changed from atrial septum secundum to atrial septum primum. Changes committed in PR #<NN>.\n","additions":1,"deletions":0},{"filePath":"/__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/PR_COMMENTS.md","relativePath":"PR_COMMENTS.md","type":"add","patch":"Index: /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/PR_COMMENTS.md\n===================================================================\n--- /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/PR_COMMENTS.md\n+++ /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/PR_COMMENTS.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,25 @@\n+## Summary\n+\n+This PR addresses issue #3522 by correcting the UBERON representation of `foramen secundum` (`UBERON:0006678`).\n+\n+## Changes\n+\n+- Updated the text definition from \"A foramen in the septum secundum\" to \"A foramen in the septum primum\".\n+- Updated the logical definition from `part_of UBERON:0004155 ! atrial septum secundum` to `part_of UBERON:0004154 ! atrial septum primum`.\n+- Added a `term_tracker_item` link to issue #3522.\n+\n+## Rationale\n+\n+The issue discussion noted that the foramen secundum/ostium secundum forms in the septum primum, not in the septum secundum. This is also consistent with the existing `atrial septum primum` definition and the existing external definition on `UBERON:0006678`, which describes it as an opening perforating the septum primum.\n+\n+## Checklist Completed\n+\n+- Read the imported issue context and repository guidance.\n+- Checked relevant existing UBERON terms: `UBERON:0006678`, `UBERON:0004154`, `UBERON:0004155`, and `UBERON:0004111`.\n+- Checked the applicable DOSDP pattern for anatomical entities that are part of another anatomical entity.\n+- Reviewed the cited Wikipedia page for foramen secundum, which states it is in the septum primum and distinguishes it from the foramen ovale in the septum secundum.\n+- Edited via `obo-checkout.pl` and `obo-checkin.pl` rather than directly editing the main ontology file.\n+- Reserialized `src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo` with `robot convert`.\n+- Validated logical consistency with `robot reason --reasoner ELK`.\n+\n+@dragon-ai-agent\n","additions":25,"deletions":0}],"diagnostics":{},"truncated":false},"title":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\nA PR_COMMENTS.md","time":{"start":1778379546395,"end":1778379546399}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_04ed8e12586166200169ffeb12b6008195a2156f3de56b46c6"}},"id":"prt_e0fae413b001Orjo9fZF9lae1P","sessionID":"ses_1f054e4cbffebD7Q6EmicnVKj8","messageID":"msg_e0fae3b4c0015OkYSg2YhD1wYN"}}
